# hyperbolicSpiral

- _hyperbolicSpiral(a=1)_

A hyperbolic spiral has a pitch angle that increases with distance from its center.

Draw:

~~~spl svg=A
(0.5 -- 6.pi).functionPlot(
	1.hyperbolicSpiral
)
~~~

